\begin_layout Lemma
\begin_inset CommandInset label
LatexCommand label
name "lem:collectionIntervalsMeasurable"

\end_inset

The following sets are generating classes for 
\begin_inset Formula $\borel\left(\R\right):$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ \left(a,\infty\right)\mid\forall a\in\R\right\} ,\ \left\{ \left[a,\infty\right)\mid\forall a\in\R\right\} ,\ \left\{ \left(-\infty,b\right)\mid\forall b\in\R\right\} ,\ \left\{ \left(-\infty,b\right]\mid\forall a\in\R\right\} .
\]

